<font color="yellow">Suami membungkuk sebagai respon pada pengantin wanita!</font>

188
00:20:04,213 --> 00:20:08,314
<font color="yellow">Hei, Nona, tidak butuh air?</font>

189
00:20:08,314 --> 00:20:10,413
<font color="yellow">Segini sudah cukup, kan?</font>

190
00:20:10,413 --> 00:20:12,413
<font color="yellow">Menurutku belum!</font>

191
00:20:14,114 --> 00:20:16,013
<font color="yellow">Lanjutkan.</font>

192
00:20:16,013 --> 00:20:18,314
<font color="yellow">Iya!</font>

193
00:20:18,314 --> 00:20:21,314
<font color="yellow">- Kipas lebih keras! Lebih keras!
- Ya!</font>

194
00:20:24,413 --> 00:20:27,314
<font color="yellow">- Jangan berhenti!
- Ya!</font>

195
00:20:27,814 --> 00:20:30,513
<font color="yellow">Hei, kubilang jangan berhenti!</font>

196
00:20:31,413 --> 00:20:33,614
<font color="yellow">Hei, minggir.</font>

197
00:20:37,213 --> 00:20:40,013
<font color="yellow">- Lebih keras!
- Aku butuh air!</font>

198
00:20:47,413 --> 00:20:49,713
<font color="yellow">Matamu terlihat lebih besar kalau dari dekat.</font>

199
00:20:52,013 --> 00:20:54,213
<font color="yellow">Hei, kelihatannya seperti kita berdua!</font>

200
00:20:54,213 --> 00:20:56,013
<font color="yellow">Iya, kan?</font>

201
00:20:56,013 --> 00:21:01,213
<font color="yellow">Satu, dua, tiga! Ayo! Ayo!</font>

202
00:21:01,213 --> 00:21:02,213
<font color="yellow">Tiga!</font>

203
00:21:02,213 --> 00:21:04,013
<font color="yellow">Tiga!</font>

204
00:21:04,513 --> 00:21:08,713
<font color="yellow">Nah, terbang!</font>

205
00:21:39,114 --> 00:21:43,314
<font color="yellow"><i>Rumah? Apa-apaan ini, mendadak seperti ini?</i></font>

206
00:21:45,213 --> 00:21:50,213
<font color="yellow">Aku ingin nikmati hari ini hanya dengan Yeon Hui.</font>

207
00:21:50,213 --> 00:21:53,013
<font color="yellow">Dan tenang berdua dengannya.</font>

208
00:21:55,213 --> 00:21:57,814
<font color="yellow">Yah, akan kucarikan, tapi...</font>

209
00:22:00,013 --> 00:22:05,314
<font color="yellow">Anu... tentang...</font>

210
00:22:05,314 --> 00:22:09,814
<font color="yellow">lilin terakhir... itu...</font>

211
00:22:09,814 --> 00:22:12,013
<font color="yellow">Tentang itu...</font>

212
00:22:12,013 --> 00:22:18,413
<font color="yellow">Sudah kudengar dari Pak Choi tentang lilin terakhir.</font>

213
00:22:21,114 --> 00:22:26,413
<font color="yellow">Aku akan nyalakan lilin terakhir Yeon Hui.</font>

214
00:22:36,114 --> 00:22:41,013
<font color="yellow">Pelan sedikit! Bukannya ada yang sedang mengejarmu!</font>

215
00:22:41,013 --> 00:22:44,013
<font color="yellow">Biarkan aku, oke?</font>

216
00:22:44,013 --> 00:22:47,314
<font color="yellow">Aku sungguh takkan bisa melalui hari ini kalau tak minum.</font>

217
00:22:47,314 --> 00:22:50,314
<font color="yellow">Sebenarnya ada apa?</font>

218
00:22:52,413 --> 00:22:55,814
<font color="yellow">Aku mengutuk Surga!</font>

219
00:22:55,814 --> 00:22:59,013
<font color="yellow">Takdir yang sungguh sial!</font>

220
00:22:59,013 --> 00:23:02,614
<font color="yellow">Aku merasa tak enak dengan Seo Ri, apalagi Heo Joon!</font>

221
00:23:02,614 --> 00:23:04,413
<font color="yellow">Ada apa ini?</font>

222
00:23:07,013 --> 00:23:10,814
<font color="yellow">Ayolah. Lukamu bahkan belum sembuh.</font>

223
00:23:10,814 --> 00:23:16,614
<font color="yellow">Lukaku? Maksudmu luka di sekujur tubuhku?</font>

224
00:23:16,614 --> 00:23:20,013
<font color="yellow">Aku sudah sering hampir mati!</font>

225
00:23:29,614 --> 00:23:33,814
<font color="yellow">Permisi! Aku tak mau makanan! Aku mau alkohol!</font>

226
00:23:33,814 --> 00:23:36,513
<font color="yellow">Hei, tenanglah! Akan kuambilkan.</font>

227
00:23:42,713 --> 00:23:47,814
<font color="yellow">Sebaiknya hargailah nyawamu jika selamat dari kematian.</font>

228
00:23:50,713 --> 00:23:53,413
<font color="yellow">Bicara denganku?</font>

229
00:24:03,213 --> 00:24:11,114
<font color="yellow">Takdir yang menyedihkan jika salah satu dari keduanya harus mati.</font>

230
00:24:11,114 --> 00:24:14,013
<font color="yellow">Ya, tentu, semua akan mati. Ya.</font>

231
00:24:26,213 --> 00:24:29,013
<font color="yellow">Obat Pengorbanan.</font>

232
00:24:29,013 --> 00:24:30,413
<font color="yellow">Obat Pengorbanan?</font>

233
00:24:30,413 --> 00:24:32,413
<font color="yellow">Berikan pada pria itu.</font>

234
00:24:33,713 --> 00:24:37,814
<font color="yellow">Dia akan sanggup mati tanpa merasa sakit.</font>

235
00:24:39,413 --> 00:24:43,513
<font color="yellow">Hanya ini yang bisa kulakukan.</font>

236
00:24:46,713 --> 00:24:52,913
<font color="yellow">Dana katakan padanya jangan putus asa.</font>

237
00:24:52,913 --> 00:25:02,213
<font color="yellow">Pengorbanannya akan menyelamatkan ratusan -- bukan, ribuan-- nyawa.</font>

238
00:25:11,114 --> 00:25:12,614
<font color="yellow">Anu...</font>

239
00:27:33,614 --> 00:27:36,614
<font color="yellow">Ke sini mau mencoba menghentikanku lagi?</font>

240
00:27:37,713 --> 00:27:41,114
<font color="yellow">Aku sudah kehilangan semua yang bisa kugunakan untuk melawanmu</font>

241
00:27:41,114 --> 00:27:43,614
<font color="yellow">mana mungkin bisa menghentikanmu?</font>

242
00:27:45,413 --> 00:27:50,413
<font color="yellow">Bagaimanapun, aku kemari untuk mengatakan sesuatu.</font>

243
00:27:50,413 --> 00:27:52,713
<font color="yellow">Tak ada yang perlu kudengarkan darimu.</font>

244
00:27:52,713 --> 00:27:55,513
<font color="yellow">Sudah dengar tentang halaman terakhir Kutukan Grimoire?</font>

245
00:27:58,213 --> 00:28:00,614
<font color="yellow">Belum, ya?</font>

246
00:28:01,713 --> 00:28:05,013
<font color="yellow">Yah, sudah diduga.</font>

247
00:28:05,013 --> 00:28:08,614
<font color="yellow">Lagipula, Pak Choi sengaja menyembunyikannya darimu.</font>

248
00:28:12,314 --> 00:28:18,614
<font color="yellow">Hanya pengorbanan cinta sejati bisa menyalakan lilin terakhir.</font>

249
00:28:18,614 --> 00:28:21,713
<font color="yellow">Itu isi halaman terakhirnya.</font>

250
00:28:23,413 --> 00:28:27,114
<font color="yellow">Benar. Mungkin pria itu orangnya, Heo Joon.</font>

251
00:28:27,114 --> 00:28:30,013
<font color="yellow">Dialah yang akan menyalakan lilin terakhirnya.</font>

252
00:28:30,013 --> 00:28:35,013
<font color="yellow">Pasti Heo Joon akan mengorbankan hidupnya demi dirimu tanpa berpikir dua kali.</font>

253
00:28:38,513 --> 00:28:41,413
<font color="yellow">Bohong.</font>

254
00:28:41,413 --> 00:28:45,614
<font color="yellow">Pasti kau membayangkan selamanya bersamanya.</font>

255
00:28:45,614 --> 00:28:47,913
<font color="yellow">Sungguh memalukan, ya.</font>

256
00:28:54,114 --> 00:28:56,314
<font color="yellow">Aku tak percaya padamu.</font>

257
00:29:08,314 --> 00:29:12,013
<font color="yellow"><i>Benar. Mungkin pria itu orangnya, Heo Joon.</i></font>

258
00:29:12,013 --> 00:29:15,114
<font color="yellow"><i>Dialah yang akan menyalakan lilin terakhirnya.</i></font>

259
00:29:15,114 --> 00:29:20,513
<font color="yellow"><i>Pasti Heo Joon akan mengorbankan hidupnya demi dirimu tanpa berpikir dua kali.</i></font>

260
00:29:20,513 --> 00:29:26,513
<font color="yellow">Jangan khawatir. Sudha kutemukan orang yang bisa menyalakan lilin terakhirnya.</font>

261
00:29:50,513 --> 00:29:52,114
<font color="yellow">Yeon Hui.</font>

262
00:29:53,614 --> 00:29:56,114
<font color="yellow">Habis dari mana, tidak memberitahuku?</font>

263
00:29:56,114 --> 00:29:58,213
<font color="yellow">Aku khawatir karena kau tiba-tiba menghilang!</font>

264
00:29:58,213 --> 00:30:00,413
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau--</font>

265
00:30:03,314 --> 00:30:07,413
<font color="yellow">Ada... apa? Sesuatu terjadi?</font>

266
00:30:08,013 --> 00:30:10,213
<font color="yellow">Kau merasa tak sehat?</font>

267
00:30:23,513 --> 00:30:26,314
<font color="yellow">Apa karena lilinnya?</font>

268
00:30:26,314 --> 00:30:29,314
<font color="yellow">Kau mengkhawatirkan lilin terakhir?</font>

269
00:30:40,513 --> 00:30:44,913
<font color="yellow">Jangan khawatir. Kita pasti bisa menyalakannya.</font>

270
00:30:44,913 --> 00:30:47,114
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana caranya?</font>

271
00:30:48,513 --> 00:30:51,513
<font color="yellow">Kau mau mati menggantikanku?</font>

272
00:30:54,314 --> 00:30:55,513
<font color="yellow">Yeon Hui.</font>

273
00:30:55,513 --> 00:30:57,913
<font color="yellow">Kau harusnya lari saja.</font>

274
00:30:59,114 --> 00:31:01,713
<font color="yellow">Katanya kau harus mati.</font>

275
00:31:03,114 --> 00:31:06,614
<font color="yellow">Mungkin akulah penyebab kau mati.</font>

276
00:31:08,213 --> 00:31:12,513
<font color="yellow">Kau harusnya lari, apapun resikonya!</font>

277
00:31:19,413 --> 00:31:21,013
<font color="yellow">Yeon Hui.</font>

278
00:31:21,013 --> 00:31:22,513
<font color="yellow">Aku...</font>

279
00:31:23,513 --> 00:31:26,314
<font color="yellow">Setelah aku kehilangan dirimu, aku...</font>

280
00:31:32,114 --> 00:31:35,713
<font color="yellow">Katanya kau mau lakukan apapun demi aku, ya kan?</font>

281
00:31:36,614 --> 00:31:40,013
<font color="yellow">Kalau begitu, pergilah.</font>

282
00:31:40,013 --> 00:31:42,213
<font color="yellow">Itu yang kuinginkan.</font>

283
00:31:47,413 --> 00:31:49,913
<font color="yellow">Aku takkan ke mana-mana.</font>

284
00:31:52,413 --> 00:31:59,913
<font color="yellow">Setelah bertemu denganmu dan bepergian bersamamu...</font>

285
00:32:01,513 --> 00:32:06,013
<font color="yellow">yang paling kutakutkan adalah...</font>

286
00:32:06,013 --> 00:32:09,314
<font color="yellow">kau mati karenaku.</font>

287
00:32:10,713 --> 00:32:17,314
<font color="yellow">Kumohon... pergilah.</font>

288
00:32:37,713 --> 00:32:39,413
<font color="yellow">Poong Yeon.</font>

289
00:32:43,413 --> 00:32:45,814
<font color="yellow">Ayah.</font>

290
00:32:47,213 --> 00:32:51,213
<font color="yellow">Aku kemari mau minta sesuatu.</font>

291
00:32:54,013 --> 00:33:03,013
<font color="yellow">Jika kutukan Yeon Hui hancur hari ini, gunakan api keramar untuk membakar Hong Joo.</font>

292
00:33:03,013 --> 00:33:10,213
<font color="yellow">Apa yang akan terjadi pada Ayah jika Hong Joo mati?</font>

293
00:33:12,713 --> 00:33:18,314
<font color="yellow">Itu yang perlu dipikirkan setelah dia menghilang.</font>

294
00:33:28,413 --> 00:33:31,314
<font color="yellow">Tak perlu mengkhawatirkanku.</font>

295
00:34:09,492 --> 00:34:12,092
<font color="yellow">Joon.</font>

296
00:34:12,092 --> 00:34:14,992
<font color="yellow">Aku ingin lakukan sesuatu denganmu.</font>

297
00:34:24,393 --> 00:34:28,092
<font color="yellow">Pengantin perempuan, pengantin laki-laki, dimohon saling membungkuk.</font>

298
00:35:36,893 --> 00:35:42,092
<font color="yellow">Baiklah. Mulai sekarang, kalian adalah pengantin.</font>

299
00:35:48,291 --> 00:35:51,791
<font color="yellow">Nah, selanjutnya.</font>

300
00:35:54,692 --> 00:35:57,393
<font color="yellow">Tunggu, sepertinya ada yang terlupakan.</font>

301
00:36:01,692 --> 00:36:03,592
<font color="yellow">Sebentar.</font>

302
00:36:27,492 --> 00:36:29,992
<font color="yellow">Rahib.</font>

303
00:36:34,192 --> 00:36:47,291
<font color="yellow">Kuharap setidaknya aku punya waktu sehari lagi dengan Joon.</font>

304
00:37:44,492 --> 00:37:48,393
<font color="yellow">Kita resmi menikah sekarang.</font>

305
00:37:51,192 --> 00:37:54,092
<font color="yellow">Sekarang kau takkan bisa lepas dariku, oke?</font>

306
00:37:59,291 --> 00:38:02,592
<font color="yellow">Aku sungguh suka padamu, Yeon Hui.</font>

307
00:38:06,791 --> 00:38:09,092
<font color="yellow">Aku juga.</font>

308
00:38:18,692 --> 00:38:22,592
<font color="yellow">Kuingin berjalan di sisimu selamanya.</font>

309
00:38:22,592 --> 00:38:24,692
<font color="yellow">Ayo keluar.</font>

310
00:38:33,791 --> 00:38:38,492
<font color="yellow">Waktu Yeon Hui tinggal sedikit.</font>

311
00:38:50,393 --> 00:38:55,492
<font color="yellow">Maaf, Tuan Heo.</font>

312
00:39:55,492 --> 00:39:59,492
<font color="yellow"><i>Di waktu aku bekerja keras demi menyelamatkanmu</i></font>

313
00:39:59,492 --> 00:40:02,291
<font color="yellow"><i>kujalani hidup semata-mata karenamu</i></font>

314
00:40:02,291 --> 00:40:07,492
<font color="yellow"><i>dan kuingin jadi seseorang yang bisa menyelamatkan dia yang kusayang.</i></font>

315
00:40:13,791 --> 00:40:19,291
<font color="yellow"><i>Yang tertinggal saat ini hanya perasaan tulusku tak ingin mati.</i></font>

316
00:40:21,492 --> 00:40:29,092
<font color="yellow"><i>Kuhanya berharap ketulusanku tidak kurang, demi kebaikanmu.</i></font>

317
00:41:18,893 --> 00:41:23,291
<font color="yellow">Heo Joon! Seo Ri!</font>

318
00:41:23,291 --> 00:41:25,092
<font color="yellow">Tuan Heo!</font>

319
00:41:26,893 --> 00:41:29,291
<font color="yellow">Seo Ri! Seo Ri!</font>

320
00:41:36,291 --> 00:41:37,893
<font color="yellow">Tuan Heo!</font>

321
00:41:38,492 --> 00:41:41,092
<font color="yellow">Tuan Heo! Tuan Heo!</font>

322
00:41:47,192 --> 00:41:48,393
<font color="yellow">Hah?</font>

323
00:42:00,592 --> 00:42:02,492
<font color="yellow">Tuan Heo...</font>

324
00:42:12,393 --> 00:42:14,393
<font color="yellow"><i>Joon.</i></font>

325
00:42:14,393 --> 00:42:19,893
<font color="yellow"><i>Semoga rasa sakitmu hanya sedikit, dan rindumu padaku hanya sedikit.</i></font>

326
00:42:22,393 --> 00:42:25,492
<font color="yellow">Yeon Hui!</font>

327
00:42:27,192 --> 00:42:30,291
<font color="yellow"><i>Aku sangat menikmati hari-hari di saat kita bersama...</i></font>

328
00:42:30,291 --> 00:42:34,192
<font color="yellow"><i>hari yang takkan pernah kumiliki lagi.</i></font>

329
00:42:44,791 --> 00:42:47,192
<font color="yellow">Yeon Hui.</font>

330
00:42:48,291 --> 00:42:50,893
<font color="yellow">Yeon Hui!</font>

331
00:42:57,592 --> 00:43:00,592
<font color="yellow"><i>Kuyakin jika kenanganmu tentang saat kita berdua</i></font>

332
00:43:00,592 --> 00:43:03,092
<font color="yellow"><i>akan berubah jadi kerinduan penuh gairah</i></font>

333
00:43:03,092 --> 00:43:05,791
<font color="yellow"><i>yang akan kita temui lagi.</i></font>

334
00:43:12,791 --> 00:43:16,092
<font color="yellow"><i>Terima kasih atas segalanya.</i></font>

335
00:43:25,692 --> 00:43:28,393
<font color="yellow"><i>Aku menyayangimu, Joon.</i></font>

336
00:44:12,192 --> 00:44:14,492
<font color="yellow">Kenapa menatapku seperti itu?</font>

337
00:44:16,692 --> 00:44:23,791
<font color="yellow">Senang melihatku mati? Kau bahagia?</font>

338
00:44:23,791 --> 00:44:25,592
<font color="yellow">Kau merasa puas?</font>

339
00:44:29,692 --> 00:44:34,692
<font color="yellow">Tatapan... matamu tampak seperti itu.</font>

340
00:44:35,692 --> 00:44:40,791
<font color="yellow">"Kasihan, gadis malang."</font>

341
00:44:40,791 --> 00:44:45,992
<font color="yellow">"Banyak yang kau lalui, tapi masih berani menjalani hidup."</font>

342
00:44:45,992 --> 00:44:49,592
<font color="yellow">"Ya, tentu. Kau harus hidup."</font>

343
00:44:49,592 --> 00:44:51,992
<font color="yellow">"Kau bsia apa lagi, selain hidup?"</font>

344
00:44:54,692 --> 00:44:56,592
<font color="yellow">"Sekarang semua berakhir."</font>

345
00:44:56,592 --> 00:44:59,492
<font color="yellow">Mau bilang begitu?</font>

346
00:44:59,492 --> 00:45:10,893
<font color="yellow">Bukan... sakit ini... kutukan ini... takkan berakhir begitu saja karena kumati.</font>

347
00:45:10,893 --> 00:45:16,692
<font color="yellow">Menurutmu semua salahku hingga negeri ini jadi begini?</font>

348
00:45:18,291 --> 00:45:24,192
<font color="yellow">Selama Surga mengamanatkan untuk menentukan pemimpin tanah ini</font>

349
00:45:24,192 --> 00:45:28,492
<font color="yellow">dan selama masih ada orang yang mengikuti tanpa berpikir, seperti domba</font>

350
00:45:28,492 --> 00:45:31,092
<font color="yellow">rakyat akan terus menderita hingga napas terakhir mereka</font>

351
00:45:31,092 --> 00:45:37,791
<font color="yellow">selama ratusan dan ribuan tahun</font>

352
00:45:37,791 --> 00:45:41,791
<font color="yellow">dan akan terus hidup dalam kesengsaraan!</font>

353
00:46:02,492 --> 00:46:06,893
<font color="yellow">Pak Choi... Pak Choi.</font>

354
00:46:20,291 --> 00:46:26,492
<font color="yellow">Sepertinya kita semua menjalani hidup penuh kutukan.</font>

355
00:47:12,791 --> 00:47:15,492
<font color="yellow">Sakit?</font>

356
00:47:19,592 --> 00:47:23,893
<font color="yellow">Itulah sakit yang kuderita</font>

357
00:47:23,893 --> 00:47:26,893
<font color="yellow">dan sakit yang kubuat mereka menderita.</font>

358
00:47:30,492 --> 00:47:39,791
<font color="yellow">Hong Joo. Dosa kita tak bisa diampuni.</font>

359
00:47:41,492 --> 00:47:45,492
<font color="yellow">Terimalah kutukannya, dan pergilah.</font>

360
00:47:45,492 --> 00:47:48,492
<font color="yellow">Aku akan pergi dengamu.</font>

361
00:49:05,893 --> 00:49:07,791
<font color="yellow">Ayah.</font>

362
00:49:08,592 --> 00:49:10,592
<font color="yellow">Ayah!</font>

363
00:49:36,893 --> 00:49:39,393
<font color="yellow">Ayah!</font>

364
00:49:40,592 --> 00:49:44,393
<font color="yellow">Ayah!</font>

365
00:51:43,692 --> 00:51:45,791
<font color="yellow">Selanjutnya!</font>

366
00:51:47,791 --> 00:51:51,992
<font color="yellow">Ini. Namaku Heo Joon.</font>

367
00:51:52,092 --> 00:51:54,492
<font color="yellow">Tes pelajaran apa yang kau ikuti?</font>

368
00:51:54,492 --> 00:51:57,592
<font color="yellow">Bermacam-macam.</font>

369
00:52:15,791 --> 00:52:18,492
<font color="yellow">Mulai!</font>

370
00:53:28,092 --> 00:53:31,592
<font color="yellow">- Dia keluar!
- Dia keluar!</font>

371
00:53:32,092 --> 00:53:37,192
<font color="yellow">- Tuan Heo!
- Hei!</font>

372
00:53:38,092 --> 00:53:40,192
<font color="yellow">Kenapa dia sudah keluar?</font>

373
00:53:41,393 --> 00:53:43,092
<font color="yellow">Ekspresi di wajahnya tak menyenangkan.</font>

374
00:53:43,092 --> 00:53:44,092
<font color="yellow">Ya.</font>

375
00:53:44,092 --> 00:53:45,893
<font color="yellow">Apakah dia sudah menyerah?</font>

376
00:53:45,893 --> 00:53:48,092
<font color="yellow">Apakah terlalu sulit?</font>

377
00:53:48,692 --> 00:53:53,092
<font color="yellow">Oh, tak apa! Senyumlah! Yang begini sering terjadi.</font>

378
00:53:53,092 --> 00:53:55,692
<font color="yellow">Jangan terlalu depresi hanya karena gagal satu ujian, oke?</font>

379
00:53:55,692 --> 00:53:59,393
<font color="yellow">Aku traktir makan hari ini, makanlah sesukamu, oke?</font>

380
00:54:03,791 --> 00:54:07,592
<font color="yellow">Maaf. Aku mau temui seseorang hari ini.</font>

381
00:54:07,592 --> 00:54:09,992
<font color="yellow">Lain kali saja kita minum.</font>

382
00:54:12,092 --> 00:54:15,893
<font color="yellow">Ya. Selalu ada tahun depan juga. Dan tahun setelahnya juga!</font>

383
00:54:15,893 --> 00:54:17,791
<font color="yellow">Ikut lagi saja tahun depan.</font>

384
00:54:19,291 --> 00:54:22,592
<font color="yellow">Sebentar. "Sesukamu?"</font>

385
00:54:22,592 --> 00:54:26,592
<font color="yellow">Kau harus simpan uang, jangan terlalu baik pada orang lain!</font>

386
00:54:26,592 --> 00:54:28,291
<font color="yellow">Memangnya kedai minumanmu? Kan, punyaku!</font>

387
00:54:28,291 --> 00:54:30,791
<font color="yellow">- Bukan, punya kita!
- Dih.</font>

388
00:54:30,791 --> 00:54:34,692
<font color="yellow">- Tunggu!
- Duh.</font>

389
00:54:41,592 --> 00:54:43,192
<font color="yellow">Tuan.</font>

390
00:54:46,592 --> 00:54:49,291
<font color="yellow">Kupikir aku takkan bisa bertemu denganmu sebelum kupergi.</font>

391
00:54:49,291 --> 00:54:50,992
<font color="yellow">Senang bertemu denganmu.</font>

392
00:54:52,092 --> 00:54:55,592
<font color="yellow">Katanya kau ikut ujian kerajaan untuk jadi dokter.</font>

393
00:54:55,791 --> 00:55:00,592
<font color="yellow">Ya. Kuingin penuhi janjiku pada Yeon Hui.</font>

394
00:55:00,592 --> 00:55:04,492
<font color="yellow">Baiklah. Kuyakin kau pasti bisa.</font>

395
00:55:04,492 --> 00:55:07,893
<font color="yellow">Tuan! Ayo berangkat!</font>

396
00:55:11,092 --> 00:55:14,393
<font color="yellow">Sungguh Tuan harus pergi?</font>

397
00:55:14,393 --> 00:55:19,492
<font color="yellow">Kuingin keluar sana dan mempelajari hal baru, dan menolong orang.</font>

398
00:55:19,492 --> 00:55:23,393
<font color="yellow">Aku merasa sepertinya itu tujuan hidup.</font>

399
00:55:28,393 --> 00:55:30,992
<font color="yellow">Semoga sehat selalu.</font>

400
00:55:31,791 --> 00:55:33,393
<font color="yellow">Terima kasih.</font>

401
00:55:37,791 --> 00:55:40,092
<font color="yellow">Baiklah, ayo!</font>

402
00:56:04,692 --> 00:56:07,393
<font color="yellow">Yang Mulia.</font>

403
00:56:08,893 --> 00:56:15,592
<font color="yellow">Heo Joon. Pakaian ini sungguh tak cocok denganmu.</font>

404
00:56:16,692 --> 00:56:22,393
<font color="yellow">Yah, kalau begini, senang bertemu denganmu lagi.</font>

405
00:56:23,291 --> 00:56:28,692
<font color="yellow">Ya, Yang Mulia. Hamba juga senang.</font>

406
00:56:33,092 --> 00:56:38,291
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana bisa seseorang sepertimu jadi dokter?</font>

407
00:56:38,291 --> 00:56:42,291
<font color="yellow">Hamba ingin tulis sebuah buku sebelum mati.</font>

408
00:56:42,291 --> 00:56:47,492
<font color="yellow">Buku yan bisa membantu mengobati orang dan menyentuh hati mereka.</font>

409
00:56:47,492 --> 00:56:49,791
<font color="yellow">Buku?</font>

410
00:56:49,791 --> 00:56:52,692
<font color="yellow">Hamba sendirian tak bisa merawat semua orang di dunia ini</font>

411
00:56:52,692 --> 00:56:57,791
<font color="yellow">tapi hamba yakin sebuah buku bisa menolong orang sakit.</font>

412
00:56:58,492 --> 00:57:02,492
<font color="yellow">Sama seperti hamba menolong Yang Mulia.</font>

413
00:57:02,492 --> 00:57:05,992
<font color="yellow">Tidak perlu.</font>

414
00:57:16,791 --> 00:57:20,592
<font color="yellow">Heo Joon, dokterku!</font>

415
00:57:22,092 --> 00:57:26,492
<font color="yellow">Aku pasti ingin membaca bukumu sebelum kumati.</font>

416
00:58:44,492 --> 00:58:48,192
<font color="yellow">Dia beri makan mereka yang lapar...</font>

417
00:58:48,192 --> 00:58:49,192
<font color="yellow"><i>[40 Tahun Kemudian]</i></font>

418
00:58:49,192 --> 00:58:52,092
<font color="yellow">dan melepaskan mereka yang keliru ditahan.</font>

419
00:58:52,092 --> 00:58:58,092
<font color="yellow">Itu sebabnya, banyak orang menyebut Im Kkeok Jung pria hebat.</font>

420
00:58:58,092 --> 00:59:00,893
<font color="yellow">- Wah!
- Wah!</font>

421
00:59:04,092 --> 00:59:06,092
<font color="yellow">- Ya?
- Kakek!</font>

422
00:59:06,092 --> 00:59:10,291
<font color="yellow">Aku ingin jadi orang hebat, seperti Im Kkeok Jung!</font>

423
00:59:10,291 --> 00:59:12,692
<font color="yellow">- Dan ikut seni bela diri dan sejenisnya?
- Ya!</font>

424
00:59:12,692 --> 00:59:15,492
<font color="yellow">Lagipula aku harus memberi pelajaran pada orang jahat!</font>

425
00:59:18,393 --> 00:59:19,692
<font color="yellow">Ya?</font>

426
00:59:19,692 --> 00:59:26,992
<font color="yellow">Aku ingin jadi dokter hebat seperti Kakek! Bagaimana caranya?</font>

427
00:59:28,092 --> 00:59:32,092
<font color="yellow">Yah, kita lihat nanti. Doter yang baik, ya?</font>

428
00:59:33,791 --> 00:59:42,791
<font color="yellow">Dokter yang baik melihat hati seseorang lebih dulu, bukan tubuhnya.</font>

429
00:59:42,791 --> 00:59:45,291
<font color="yellow">- Hatinya?
- Ya.</font>

430
00:59:45,291 --> 00:59:51,893
<font color="yellow">Kau harus pandai membaca hati seseorang agar jadi dokter yang baik.</font>

431
00:59:52,492 --> 00:59:54,291
<font color="yellow">Paham?</font>

432
00:59:54,291 --> 00:59:56,393
<font color="yellow">- Ya!
- Ya!</font>

433
00:59:56,393 --> 00:59:57,393
<font color="yellow">Paham?</font>

434
00:59:57,393 --> 00:59:59,592
<font color="yellow">- Ya!
- Ya!</font>

435
01:00:02,492 --> 01:00:05,893
<font color="yellow">- Tuan.
- Ya.</font>

436
01:00:27,092 --> 01:00:29,992
<font color="yellow"><i>[Dongui Bogam:
Contoh Obat-Obatan Korea]</i></font>

437
01:00:31,492 --> 01:00:36,092
<font color="yellow">Akhirnya selesai, Tuan!</font>

438
01:00:36,092 --> 01:00:38,592
<font color="yellow">Sungguh mengagumkan.</font>

439
01:00:38,592 --> 01:00:42,893
<font color="yellow">Tapi, Tuan. Aku ingin tanya sesuatu.</font>

440
01:00:42,893 --> 01:00:45,092
<font color="yellow">Apa?</font>

441
01:00:45,092 --> 01:00:49,092
<font color="yellow">Ada tertulis dalam Dongui Bogam.</font>

442
01:00:49,092 --> 01:00:52,692
<font color="yellow">Membahas tentang ramuan agar bisa melihat hantu, atau membuat jatuh cinta.</font>

443
01:00:52,692 --> 01:00:56,492
<font color="yellow">Itu bukan bagian dari ilmu medis.</font>

444
01:00:58,592 --> 01:01:03,492
<font color="yellow">Itu ramuan yang temanku buat, tapi ya. Bukan ilmu medis.</font>

445
01:01:07,092 --> 01:01:09,893
<font color="yellow">Sudah siap ke kota?</font>

446
01:01:09,893 --> 01:01:11,393
<font color="yellow">Ya, Tuan.</font>

447
01:01:11,393 --> 01:01:14,992
<font color="yellow">Kalau begitu, ayo cepat.</font>

448
01:01:55,492 --> 01:01:58,592
<font color="yellow">Istirahat sebentar dulu sebelum lanjut.</font>

449
01:01:58,592 --> 01:02:00,791
<font color="yellow">Ya, Tuan.</font>

